Activity Logger

The [prgm]now[/prgm] command tracks what you're working on throughout the day.

$ [prgm]now[/prgm]                                # Show today's entries
$ [prgm]now[/prgm] [arg-value]Working on feature X @project[/arg-value]  # Log current activity
$ [prgm]now[/prgm] [arg]--since[/arg] [arg-value]14:30[/arg-value] [arg-value]Meeting @project[/arg-value]   # Log past activity
$ [prgm]now[/prgm] [arg]--show[/arg] [arg-value]2025-12-15[/arg-value]              # View specific day

Tag projects with [bold]@project-name[/bold] to generate timesheets automatically.
